<h1 class="mb-2 font-bold text-2xl"> 🔊 About Audio 🔊 </h1>

<h2 id="goals" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Goals</h2>
<p>Our game audio should</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
    <li>Capture the feeling of goin on a grand adventure</li>
    <li>Create an uplifiting, active atmosphere</li>
    <li>Avoid being jarring or distracting from gameplay</li>
</ul>
<p class="mt-2">We initially planned to have four audio tracks for the game:</p>
<ul class="list-disc ml-8">
    <li>The Great Hall</li>
    <li>The Main Level (The Cellar)</li>
    <li>A Boss Encounter</li>
    <li>A Main Theme</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="inspiration" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-4">Inspiration</h2>
<p>We had a few key inspirations for audio.</p>
